com.paypal.selion.platform.mobile.ios

Class UIAElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.mobile.ios.UIAElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MobileElement, UIAutomationElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UIAAlert, UIAButton, UIAImage, UIAList, UIANavigationBar, UIAPicker, UIASlider, UIAStaticText, UIASwitch, UIATableView, UIATextField

    public class UIAElement
extends Object
implements UIAutomationElement, MobileElement
    The UIAElement is the super class for all user interface elements in the context of the Automation instrument for automating user interface testing of iOS apps. This interface defines more general methods that can be used on any type of user interface elements.
